"lng":10.301288},{"lat":54.220315,"lng":10.300916},{"lat":54.220576,"lng":10.299665}]],"source":"hejfish_api_map_geojson","confidence":"high"},"links":{"source":"https://www.hejfish.com/d/13119-lanker-see","hejfish":"https://www.hejfish.com/d/13119-lanker-see","alleangeln":null,"image":"https://file.hejfish.com/image/cc1200x900/4f/38/4f38bbda391cfba60dbf4da233a40819a40706dc.jpeg"},"fish":["Div. Weißfische","Karpfen","Hecht","Flussbarsch","Zander","Aal","Wels","Schleie"],"metadata":{"platform":"hejfish","geocode_source":"hejfish_api_map_geojson","slug":"lanker-see","seo_name":"Lanker See","description":"<p><b>Lanker See</b><br></p> <p>Größe: ca. 200 ha<br>Der Lanker See wird von der Schwentine durchflossen und ist so mit vielen weiteren Seen im Kreis Plön direkt oder indirekt verbunden. Neben den vielen Weißfischen sind auch hier Karpfen, Hecht, Barsch, Zander, Aal und Welse zu fangen.</p> <p><b>Freudenholmer Bucht</b><br></p> <p>Größe: ca. 24 ha<br>Die Freudenholmer Bucht ist ein Teil des Lanker See und besitzt <u><i><b>eigene</b></i></u> Fischereirechte. </p> <p><b>Die Freudenholmer Bucht ist für unsere Gäste derzeit nicht nutzbar! </b></p>","borders":"<p>Gewässer-Grenze entnehmen Sie dem PDF.</p>\n\n<p>Geo-Daten: </p>\n\n<ul><li>Zugangstor zum Vereinsgelände Castöhlenweg (54.219547, 10.282788)</li><li>Parkplatz am Lanker See (Vereinsgelände Castöhlenweg) Parkplatz für Gast-Angler mit PKW (54.220343, 10.281190)</li></ul>","techniques":["Ansitzangeln","Feedern","Friedfischangeln","Karpfenangeln","Posenangeln","Raubfischangeln","Spinnangeln"],"rules_text":"<p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:11.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:\r\n2;background:white\"><b><span style=\"font-family:\">Angelbedingungen</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:11.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:\r\n2;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\">Tageskarte gilt von 30 Minuten vor Sonnenaufgang bis 30 Minuten nach Sonnenuntergang. Ruderboot mit Kennzeichen des ASV Preetz -&gt; nur vom Gelände Lanker See.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:11.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:\r\n2;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 18pt;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Neben den gesetzlichen Bedingungen gelten noch weitere nachfolgend aufgeführte:</span></p><ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\"><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Die Verwendung und das Mitführen von Echoloten/Echolotgebern mit Live-Sonar Technologie, die geeignet sind Bewegungen der Fische in Echtzeit darzustellen, ist verboten.</span></span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">max. 3 Angeln vom Ufer bzw. einem Ruderboot mit ASV-Kennzeichen. Je Angel 1 Haken</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Mindestmaße: Aal 50 cm, Hecht 60 cm&nbsp;ansonsten die gesetzlichen Mindestmaße gemäß Binnenfischereiverordnung des Landes Schleswig-Holstein (BiFVo, aktuellste Fassung vom 05.08.2021),&nbsp;</span><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">gekennzeichnete Fische sind umgehend beim Gewässerwart zu melden</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">untermäßige Fische sind sofort frei zu lassen</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Schonzeiten nach der gültigen BiFVo (gemäß Gesetz), der Hecht ist auch bis zum 30.04.2022 geschont</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">die Verwendung lebender Köderfische ist verboten,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">die Köderfische müssen aus dem Gewässer stammen,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">der Angelplatz bzw. das Ruderboot sind selbstverständlich immer sauber zu verlassen!</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">vom Ufer der Gewässer Lanker See, Kirchsee, Schwentine und&nbsp;</span><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">an der Hörn des Postsee darf geangelt werden</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Inseln dürfen&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u>nicht</u></span>&nbsp;betreten oder mit dem Boot angefahren werden,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Uferbewuchs darf nicht beschädigt werden, vom Reet ist Abstand zu halten,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">das Aufstellen von Zelten, sowie das Campen an den Gewässern ist untersagt, &nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">offenes Feuer ist an den Uferkanten verboten,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Hunde sind immer an der Leine zu führen,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">der Gastangler haftet für alle durch ihn entstandenen Schäden,</span><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;der ASV Preetz und Umgebung e.V. ist von jeglicher Haftung befreit.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><u style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Besondere Bestimmungen:</span></u><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Private Boote, Kajaks, Tretboote, Paddelboote, Faltboote, Schlauchboote etc. dürfen nicht zum Angeln verwendet werden.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Alle Arten von Motoren an den Ruderbooten sind verboten!</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><br></span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initi